The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Punters Corner - Arktouros has it easy
                                                                                                                       7                                                                                      Arktouros has it easy 
            STAR RACER                            
	Calcutta: Trainer Vijay Singhs 4-1 shot Arktouros fully justified his higher rating while scoring a decisive victory over the course-favourite Alacrity in the 1,200m Calcutta Monsoon Sprint, Saturdays main attraction. Jockey C. Alford also gave the topweighted horse a judicious ride  holding the five-year-old back till the final turn and coming the shortest way home.  
	RESULTS  
	1. Whispering Grass Plate: Silver Guest (C.Alford) 1, Mafia Chief (Md Sameer) 2, Honitus (Shezad) 3. NR: Mandakhni (3). Won by: 3-1/2, 4-1/2; (1-21.94). Win Rs 15; (P) 11, 14; (Q) 16; Shp: 21; (T) 62. Fav: Silver Guest. Winner trained by Vijay.          
	2. Friendly Dancer Handicap: Andrology (Vinay) 1, Andeana (B.Mahesh) 2,Validate (C.Alford) 3. Won by: 2-1/2, 2; (2-16.7). Win Rs 82; (P) 19, 15; (Q) 66; Shp: 21; (T) 216. Fav: Validate. Winner trained by Vikash. (Note: The Winner survived an objection lodged by the rider of the third horse)          
	3. Topspin Cup: Royal Ballerina (B.Mahesh) 1, Royal Scandal (Md Sameer) 2, Sun Dancer (Babu) 3. Won by: Shd, Nk; (1-21.67). Win Rs 33; (P) 12, 16, 18; (Q) 76; Shp: 38; (T) 259. Fav: Sun Dancer. Winner trained by Javed.          
	4. Rising Bell Handicap: Focus (Babu) 1, Arizzano (C.Alford) 2, Flying Jaguar (Md Sameer) 3. Won by: 3-1/4, 1-1/4; (1-13.32). Win Rs 42; (P) 15,1 5, 20; (Q) 43; Shp: 34; (T) 475. Fav: Arizzano. Winner trained by Karki.          
	5. Calcutta Monsoon Sprint: Arktouros (C.Alford) 1, Alacrity (B.Mahesh) 2, Thundering Hooves (Shailesh) 3. Won by: 2-1/2, 1/2; (1-19.15). Win Rs 34; (P) 16, 15, 17; (Q) 49; Shp: 42; (T) 216. Fav: Alacrity. Winner trained by Vijay.          
	6. Ballet Master Handicap: Roxy (Shailesh) 1, Portpatrick (Babu S.) 2, Sea Monarch (Md Sameer) 3. Won by: 2, 5, 1/2; (1-33.6). Win Rs 69; (P) 23, 29, 47; (Q) 214; Shp: 71; (T) 5,009. Fav: Requite. Winner trained by Javed.          
	Jackpot: Rs 74,237; (C) Rs 3,051.          
	Treble: (i) Rs 383; (ii) Rs 1,393.                                                                                                                                                          
